ie als Zustandsgröße Fundamentale Konzepte: Der zweite Hauptsatz Fundamentale Konzepte: Mikroskopische Deutung der Entropie Kraftwerksprozesse – Strom von der Sonne Mechanismen der Wärmeübertragung – Windchill Instationäre Wärmeleitung – Das perfekte Frühstücksei  aWhat is actually happening to that pork cutlet sizzling in the frying pan, or to the cauliflower in the pot? What are the physical and chemical processes that take place during heating? Being able to answer these questions is useful, and not only to improve our cooking. Becoming aware of the physics of cooking inevitably leads us to the actual aim of this book: understanding the laws of thermodynamics.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aMaterialsxThermal properties. 0aThermodynamics. 4aLehrbuch. 4aThermodynamik. 7aSCIENCE / Mechanics / Thermodynamics.2bisacsh  aTextbook, thermodynamics.1 aMüller, Rainer, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Physical Sciences 2000 - 2014z9783110637212oZDB-23-GPS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2013z9783110317350oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET MATHEMATIK, PHYSIK, INGENIEURWISS. 2013z9783110317275oZDB-23-DMP40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311030201140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110302011423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110302011/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MTPY  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2013  aZDB-23-DMPb2013  aZDB-23-GPSc2000d2014